notes.title: My neighbor is a vampire
notes.text:
--wears a cape
--only comes out at night
--refused my super tasty garlic bread
--says he doesn't own any mirrors bc he's practicing self-love and avoiding triggers of vanity
--i've actually never seen him eat people food
--like even when he made a big deal of the garlic bread, i didn't see him eat anything else
--slicks his hair back
--wears a cape
--says he has social anxiety and doesn't like to be around too many people 
--like his limit is six other people at a party and if any more show up, he has to "go tend to his garden"
--gives the church a wide berth on the steeple side. i noticed this the other day bc he walks to the butcher shop across the square from the church a few times a week and i realized he always seemed to take the long way around to get there.
--says his family died a long time ago
--the cape thing is super weird and the main reason i started this list

notes.title: i'm gonna be really honest
notes.text: i have no idea what i'm doing but i know that i am at least trying and for now, that's good enough.
